<plot>Documentary questioning the reliability of Lægemiddelstyrelsen (the Danish Medicines Agency). Several drugs which have been approved by Lægemiddelstyrelsen now prove to have fatal consequences for the patients who used them. The drugs Letigen and Vioxx are some of these.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?136746</url></doc>
